000009C *>
000010C *> 22/09/15 vbc - Added Param-Restrict (Access) within a current filler.
000011C *>                Set this will stop display of option Z in sub-system menus.
000012C *>                Need to detect actual user though when setup or could just use
000013C *>                chown for sys002 to admin user?
000014C *> 25/06/16 vbc - Added RDBMS-Port & needs RDBMS-Host, RDBMS-Socket.
000015C *>                Increased 'System-data' from 384 to 512 bytes & removed O/E
000016C *>                  Block (128) as it is unused.
000017C *> 26/06/16 vbc - Updated MySQL Load scripts ACASDB.sql in ACAS/mysql.
000018C *>                  Prima is yet to be done !!!
000019C *> 19/10/16 vbc - Changed PL-Approp-AC in IRS block from 9(5) to 9(6) for GL
000020C *>                support & reduced filler by 1.
000021C *>                With IRS data mapped into ACAS the IRS block can reduce to 32 bytes
000022C *>                Just need to change all of the IRS programs to use ACAS fields but
000023C *>                also NEED to change the date processing to use same in rest of ACAS
000024C *>                and not binary days since 01/01/2000 and hold dates in dd/mm/yy form.
000025C *>                Added 2 88s to Op-System for IRS.
000026C *> 27/10/16 vbc - Changed level-5 to IRS instead of omitted O/E.
000027C *> 15/01/18 vbc - Added Stats-Date-Period with a filler & vers = 14.
000028C *> 02/02/18 vbc - Replaced file-statuses with filler x(32).
000029C *> 10/02/18 vbc - For PL-Approp-AC6 move filler to beginning of field as irs
000030C *>                does not need the leading digit (uses only 5).
000031C *> 17/03/18 vbc - Added SL-Invoice-Lines within last filler so gone from 45 to 43.
000032C *> 18/03/18 vbc - Added false for Level-5 & 6, e.g., zero.
000033C *> 06/06/18 vbc - Added six new fields as bin-long to support for G-L and IRS used at same time.
000034C *>                RDBMS needs to be updated. Done 06/06/16 -> Mariadb backups.
000035C *>                sys002 needs to be updated if implemented.
000036C *>                systemMT needs to be updated (in un/load moves).
000037C *> 03/06/20 vbc - Changes to some RDBMS values.
000038C *> 10/12/22 vbc - Remove File-Duplicates-In-Use - not used.
000039C *> 14/04/23 vbc - SL-Autogen added (& PL-Autogen) both using FILLER space.
000040C *> 15/05/23 vbc - SL-Next-Rec and PL-Next-Rec bin-short unsigned for next Autogen record key.
000041C *> 26/06/23 vbc - Added Company-Email repacing filler.
000042C *> 09/09/23 vbc - Pre support for OE but as comments for now as will not be used in ACAS - pointless.
000043C *> 10/09/23 vbc - Removed condition Payroll-No as not used.
000044C *> 13/03/24 vbc - In fillers added fields SL-BO-Flag and Stk-BO-Active,
000045C *> 18/12/24 vbc - Clean up remd out texts & added Co. Phone No reducing filler.
000046C *> 14/11/25 vbc - Support for Payroll in use that replaces OE usage as not needed.
