000297  *>
000298  *> Terminal-Sizing.
000299  *>
000300       perform  forever
000301                accept   WS-Env-Lines   from lines
000302                if       WS-Env-Lines < 28
000303                         display  SY010    at 0101 with erase eos
000304                         accept   WS-Reply at 0133
000305                         move     8 to WS-Term-Code
000306                         exit perform cycle
000307                end-if
000308                accept   WS-Env-Columns from Columns
000309                if       WS-Env-Columns < 80
000310                         display  SY013    at 0101 with erase eos
000311                         accept   WS-Reply at 0130
000312                         move     8 to WS-Term-Code
000313                         exit perform cycle
000314                end-if
000315       end-perform.
000316  *>
000317  *> Set up error message areas on screen - assumes terninal set for => 28 deep
000318  *>  and must be 80 wide   BUT only needs depth of 24 or more.
000319  *>
000320       subtract 2 from WS-Env-Lines giving WS-22-Lines.
000321       subtract 1 from WS-Env-Lines giving WS-23-Lines.
000322       move     WS-Env-Lines to WS-Lines.
000323       move     zero         to WS-Term-Code.
