000424  *>**********************************
000425  *>
000426  *>  Converts date in WSE-Date to UK/USA/Intl date format using current-date
000427  *>*************************************************************************
000428  *> Input:   WSE-Date via CURRENT-DATE
000429  *> output:  WS-Date as uk/US/Inlt date format
000430  *>
000431  *> first create in UK date
000432       move     WSE-Year  to WS-Year.
000433       move     WSE-Month to WS-Month.
000434       move     WSE-Days  to WS-Days.
000435
000436  *>
000437       if       Date-Form = zero
000438                move 1 to Date-Form.
000439  *>
000440       if       Date-UK          *> nothing to do as in UK format
000441                go to zz070-Exit.
000442       if       Date-USA                *> Swap month and days
000443                move WS-Days  to WS-Swap
000444                move WS-Month to WS-Days
000445                move WS-Swap  to WS-Month
000446                go to zz070-Exit.
000447  *>
000448  *> So its International date format
000449  *>
000450       move     "ccyy/mm/dd" to WS-Date.  *> Swap to Intl
000451       move     WSE-Year  to WS-Intl-Year.
000452       move     WSE-Month to WS-Intl-Month.
000453       move     WSE-Days  to WS-Intl-Days.
000454  *>
000455   zz070-Exit.
000456       exit     section.
000457  *>


